THIS WAS THE WORST FUCKING MOVIE EVER MADE!!!!! I laughed so hard in the first anchorman that I almost peed myself. I didn't laugh a single fucking time in this movie. Not once. not a giggle. Not a smirk.

This movie was a fucking disaster. You know that feeling you get after waking up from one of those REALLY twisted dreams, that feeling like: "why in the fuck would I dream about that twisted shit?" and it makes you sick to your stomach and ruins your whole day? that's what this movie will do to you.
